feedback_text: I've worked with Jacob a few times before, but we got a chance to really get to understand how vector databases and RAG can be used to increase voice quality output. This was a great project because we are working on similar projects. Talking with him helped me get a much better understanding of how everything works together and from that conversation I realized that I should taking fine tuning into account to improve output quality of my AI assistant. Not only would that give better context to the what the LLM is trying to achieve, but I can train the LLM on past user conversations! Jake is talented and always challenges me on what I really know. This is great because it makes me reflect on how well I know a topic and how much more I need to learn about a topic. Always great conversations with Jake!
summary:
Strengths: In-depth knowledge of vector databases and RAG. Challenges the recipient to reflect and learn more.

Opportunities: Consider providing more specific examples of how to fine-tune output quality.

Additional Comments: Great collaborative spirit and mutual learning experience with Jake.
